task.summary: Changed from using badlogic to jbox2d
Updated so client and server only communicate through Strings using endpoints
Added ability to change player direction and tyrus so client can run
Added compression for sending info from server
Updated onMessage to use single method
Updated server to use ArrayList of players
Updated Endpoints to make pushing to heroku easier
Added ping request and updated to use ByteBuffer rather than Byte[]
Fixed game crash on server startup
More zombies and they stop if there are no players
Added username to player and changed client's player's color
Added player health and zombie attack power
Added a map background to make seeing movement easier
Added PPM to fix max speed issue
Added the ability to shoot and kill zombies
Updated shooting to shot in direction player is moving
Added player/ zombie images and fixed bounds
Updated image managed to handle rotations
Added player sprite for walking and running animation
